<SLUG> BC-Pakistan-Bus accident,0091 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Pakistani bus careens out of control killing 15 people
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   ISLAMABAD, Pakistan (AP) _ A bus careened off a mountain road
killing 15 people and injuring another 40 others, according to news
reports Wednesday.
	   The bus, overloaded with nearly 70 people, crashed near Swabi in
northwest Pakistan on Tuesday, the independent English-language
newspaper The News reported.
	   The bus apparently was speeding when the driver lost control,
the newspaper reported.
	   The accident was under investigated. 	   
