<SLUG> BC-Sports-Baseball-NL Leaders,0390 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
TUESDAY'S MAJOR LEAGUE LEADERS
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; By The Associated Press &QC; 
 &UR; NATIONAL LEAGUE &QC; 

