Nokia to expand further in China with new factory
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   HELSINKI, Finland (AP) _ Finnish telecommunications group Nokia
will build a new plant in the eastern Chinese province of Jiangsu,
to make digital mobile phone base stations and equipment, the
company said Wednesday.
