 &UR; By BARRY HATTON &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   LISBON, Portugal (AP) _ A parliamentary delegation scheduled a
meeting Wednesday with renegade soldiers holed up in a military
installation since launching a coup attempt four days ago in this
