<HEADLINE>
BCI urges President to initiate dialogue on national issues, THE INDEPENDENT
</HEADLINE>
BCI urges President to initiate dialogue on national issues, THE INDEPENDENT &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   THE INDEPENDENT
   BANGLADESH
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

