<SLUG> BC-South Africa-Chemical Warfare, 2nd Ld </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Mandela was target for chemical disabling, scientist alleges
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; Eds: RESTORES ``By'' in byline &QL; 
 &UR; By PAUL HARRIS &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

<TEXT>
	   CAPE TOWN, South Africa (AP) _ Officials in the apartheid-era
government plotted to mentally disable Nelson Mandela with poison
during the final years of his imprisonment and shortly thereafter,
a former government scientist testified Wednesday.
 &UR; There was, 2nd graf pvs
</TEXT>
(PROFILE
(WS SL:BC-South Africa-Chemical Warfare, 2nd Ld; CT:i; 
(REG:EURO;)
(REG:BRIT;)
