	   DMIB Bhd has launched an air-steriliser product that claims to
virtually eliminate all presence of germs in the air. ``The
Germitol Air Steriliser works by purifying and sterilising the air
to give you a 99.91 per cent germ-free environment, as proven in
independent studies conducted by reputable microbiology
laboratories,'' said DMIB, the marketing agent, in a statement. The
Singapore-manufactured steriliser is useful for those suffering
from breathing and respiratory problems like continuous wheezing, a
stuffed nose, chronic coughing and asthma. It can also be used by
those recuperating from surgery to reduce the risk of infection.
The purification and sterilising process involves using UV-C light
and Germitrol's patented UV system which emits low level of
radiation. The Sirim-tested product is available in three models,
and comes in a compact and portable unit. It is available at Apex
Pharmacy, Handi-Mart, Carrefour or other selected pharmacies. Those
interested can also contact DMIB at 03-791-8833 ext 814/843.
	   
