<HEADLINE>
EDS: Completes results
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   HALLE, Germany (AP) _ Results Wednesday from the dlrs 875,000
Gerry Weber ATP tennis tournament (seedings in parantheses):
 &UR; Second Round &QC; 
	   Paul Haarhuis, Netherlands, def. Petr Korda (1), Czech Republic,
7-6 (7-4), 6-4.
	   Gianluca Pozzi, Italy, def. Richard Fromberg, Australia, 6-1,
7-6 (7-1).
	   Richard Krajicek (3), Netherlands, def. Tommy Haas, Germany,
3-6, 6-4, 6-1.
	   Magnus Larsson, Sweden, def. Steve Campbell, United States, 6-0,
6-3.
