	   KUALA TERENGGANU, Sun. - Two motorcyclists were killed in
separate road crashes in Kemaman and Marang yesterday.
	   They were Wan Nazrul Nizam Wan Awang, 22, of Kampung Tok Jembal,
and Adisham Idris, 15, of Kampung Alur Ketitir, Merchang.
	   Both died on the spot.
