Tengku Azman Tengku Abdullah said today that Wan Nazrul was riding
his machine when he was involved in a crash with a lorry at the
142km Jalan Kuala Terengganu- Kuantan at 11.45am.
	   In the other crash at Marang, Tengku Azman said Adisham was
killed when his machine collided with a car at the 46.5km Jalan
Kuala Terengganu- Kuantan at 9.45pm.
	   
