19 killed in shop fire, JAKARTA POST
</HEADLINE>
19 killed in shop fire, JAKARTA POST &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   JAKARTA POST
   INDONESIA
   ENGLISH
ASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

