<HEADLINE>
UK-based firm now owns 51pc of Berjaya Prudential, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
UK-based firm now owns 51pc of Berjaya Prudential, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 08, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
