<HEADLINE>
Couple robbed of car, cash and jewellery, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Couple robbed of car, cash and jewellery, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 09, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
