managing director, made a personal contribution of RM5,000. A
similiar amount was donated by Four Season Travel (Japan) while
Fuji Electric (M) Sdn donated RM1,000.
	   The donation was handed over to State Executive Councillor Datuk
Dr Kang Chin Seng at a dinner last night.
	   
