<HEADLINE>
Boarding system for excellence, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
</HEADLINE>
Boarding system for excellence, NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES &QL; 
   June 10, 1998
   NEW STRAITS TIMES-MANAGEMENT TIMES
   MALAYSIA
   ENGLISH
   R.V. VeeraASIA WorldSources, Inc. 201 PENNSYLVANIA AVENUE, S.E., 2nd Floor

