<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-Travel Section, Advisory,0158 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
EDITORS:
</HEADLINE>

<TEXT>
	   Beginning this Saturday, June 13, we will transmit a weekly
package of travel stories, illustrated with photos and/or graphics.
	   The package will include two or three feature stories from
various nations, plus a package of travel briefs.
	   We hope you will find the package useful for newspaper travel
sections and broadcast travel features.
	   Each story will be slugged BC-TRAV-, followed by a word
identifying the story, such as BC-TRAV-Stockholm.
	   The travel section is the newest addition to our daily lineup of
feature packages. The roster:
	   Monday - General features (BC-FEA-)
	   Tuesday - Business and Finance (BC-FEA-)
	   Wednesday - General features (BC-FEA-)
	   Thursday - Science and Technology (BC-SCI- or BC-MED-)
	   Friday - General features (BC-FEA-)
	   Saturday - Travel (BC-TRAV-)
	   Sunday - Arts and Entertainment (BC-ARTS-)
	   The AP 	   
</TEXT>
