<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-AP-Sports Digest, 2 Takes,0778 </SLUG>


<TEXT>
	   WORLD SPORTS AT 0000 GMT
 &UR; WORLD CUP:
	   PARIS _ Bugs on stilts and own goals. If that's any indication,
it's going to be a weird World Cup.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-World Cup Roundup. Recap expected by 0200
GMT.
	   By Brian Trusdell
	   SAINT-DENIS, France _ It wasn't Ronaldo's amazing speed or a
power-packed Roberto Carlos free kick that earned Brazil its 2-1
World Cup victory over Scotland. It was Tommy Boyd's chest.
	   Slug Sports-Soccer-Brazil-Scotland. Expected by 0200 GMT.
	   By Robert Millward
	   RIO DE JANEIRO, Brazil _ Rush hour comes early Wednesday as
Brazilians abandon work to watch their team's first appearance in
this year's televised World Cup.
