<SLUG> BC-Belarus-Sewer War,0674 </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
Deja vu in Belarus: Former Soviets and West in smelly diplomatic
</HEADLINE>
 &UR; RETRANSMITTING with photo number &QL; 
dispute &QL; 
 &UR; AP Photo MIN101 &QL; 
 &UR; By MITCHELL LANDSBERG &QC; 
 &UR; Associated Press Writer &QC; 

